#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:4
msgid "Object Origin"
msgstr "Origine d'objet"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:6
msgid ""
"Each object has an origin point. The location of this point determines where "
"the object is located in 3D space. When an object is selected, a small "
"circle appears, denoting the origin point. The location of the origin point "
"is important when translating, rotating or scaling an object. See :doc:"
"`Pivot Points </editors/3dview/object/transform/transform_control/"
"pivot_point/index>` for more."
msgstr ""
"Chaque objet a un point d'origine. L'emplacement de ce point détermine où la "
"position de l'objet dans l'espace 3D. Quand un objet est sélectionné, un "
"petit cercle apparaît, marquant le point d'origine. La position du point "
"d'origine est importante pour la translation, la rotation et le "
"dimensionnement de l'objet. Voir :doc:`Points pivot </editors/3dview/object/"
"transform/transform_control/pivot_point/index>` pour plus d'informations."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:11
msgid ""
"The color of the origin is set by the :ref:`animation-state-colors` and the "
"size can be changed in the :doc:`Interface tab </preferences/interface>` of "
"the User Preferences."
msgstr ""
"La couleur de l'origine est fixée par les :ref:`animation-state-colors` et "
"la taille peut être modifiée dans l':doc:`onglet Interface </preferences/"
"interface>` de *User Preferences*."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:16
msgid "Moving Object Centers"
msgstr "Déplacement des centres d'objet"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:18
msgid ""
"Object Centers can be moved to different positions through :menuselection:"
"`3D View editor --> Transform --> Origin` (press :kbd:`T` to open panel):"
msgstr ""
"Les centres d'objet peuvent être déplacés à des positions différentes avec :"
"menuselection:`3D View editor --> Transform --> Origin` (press :kbd:`T` pour "
"ouvrir le panneau):"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:21
msgid "Geometry to Origin"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:22
msgid ""
"Move model to origin and this way origin of the object will also be at the "
"center of the object."
msgstr ""
"Déplace le modèle à l'origine et de cette manière l'origine de l'objet sera "
"aussi au centre de l'objet."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:24
msgid "Origin to Geometry"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:24
msgid ""
"Move origin to the center of the object and this way origin of the object "
"will also be at the center of the object."
msgstr ""
"Déplace l'origine au centre de l'objet et de cette manière l'origine de "
"l'objet sera aussi au centre de l'objet."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:26
msgid "Origin to 3D Cursor"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:27
msgid "Move origin of the model to the place of the 3D cursor."
msgstr "Déplace l'origine du modèle à la position du curseur 3D."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:30
msgid "Origin to Center of Mass"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/transform/origin.rst:29
msgid "Move origin to calculated center of mass of model."
msgstr "Déplace l'origine au centre de masse calculé du modèle."
